Package: test2infeR
Type: Package
Title: R Interface to Julia HMM Diagnostic Inference
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Your", "Name", email = "your.email@example.com",
    role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: R interface to a Julia-based Hidden Markov Model (HMM) 
    inference engine for diagnostic testing data. Supports NUTS, MAP, and MLE
    estimation. The package automatically handles Julia installation and 
    provides a simple interface for running inference on test matrices.
